name: Digital You
description: CRZIKRN 2021, "Digital You" // Show your face to the camera, wave your hands, and be digitized as a work of art. Stand still so the camera can recognize your face to open up a colorful world. An interactive art piece where the art changes every time. Screenshot any moment! We live in a world where our digital avatars roam. Let's bring several screenshots of this work of us and create one big portrait of the community.
